\id JUD - Mpoto Bible Version 
\h Yuda 
\toc1 Baluwa jejalembakike na Yuda 
\toc2 Yuda 
\toc3 Yuda 
\mt2 Baluwa jejalembakiki na 
\mt1 Yuda 
\imt1 Ulongulelo 
\ip Baluwa jejilowakeka kwa lihina laka Yuda jakapekiwi lihina leniheli kubhokana na mlemba. Yuda akaliloghwi mweni ngati ndongu waka Yakobo, joakabhi ndongu waka Bambo Yesu. Bhela, Yuda ajoju apwaghakika kubha nde jumu wa bhalongu bha chikambaku bhaka Yesu (1). Ngachetumanyi ngati baluwa jenjenu jakalembakiki kwa ndandi ja kutumakika kwa likanisa limu maalumu, nambu kubhokana na kubha na malembu ghamaheli gha Lulaghilu lwa Mwande ibhonikana kubha akajilembiki baluwa heji ngati akabhalembi Bhayahude. Hata bhela baluwa jaki ajilanda, “mwehapa mwendowakiki na Chapanga na ambabhu mpalakiki na Chapanga Atati na kubhekakeka lukwale mkati jaka Yesu Kristo.” (1). Iwezikana kubha baluwa jenu jakalembakiki mu chaka cha 60 baada ja kubhelakeka kwaka Yesu Kristo. 
\ip Ndandi ja kulemba baluwa jaki kwa Bhakristo bhokapi lakabhi nde kubhalakalila ngabhihowakeka na bhabhola bha upuhe (4). Yuda akalongali matukiu ghamaheli gha Lulaghilu lwa Mwande na malandilu ghaki nahuli kuipeke hoja makile. Baluwa jenjenu jibhi na maholalelu ghamaheli gha baluwa jela jaka Petulu wa kabhele jakabya papamu na malakalilu kubhokana na bhabhola bha upuhe (4, 2 Petulu 2:1), na maholalelu aghagha ghabhalongale papamu na bhatumika bha kunani kwaka Chapanga, na michi ja Sodoma na Gomola. 
\iot Ghaghabhihomu 
\io1 Kutumbula, Yuda alongela na bhasomaji bhaki bhaakabhalembile (1-2). 
\io1 Kabhete, abhoha ndandi ja kubhalembela ambaju nde kubhalakalila kubhokana na bhabhola bha upuhe (3-4). 
\io1 Baada ja panihapa abhoha milenganesu kuhuma kwa bhandu na matukiu gha Lulaghilu lwa Mwande (5-16). 
\io1 Kabhete abhapwaghi ntundu moibhapalaki kutama baada ja kupekewa malaghalakilu hagha (17-23). 
\io1 Yuda ajomule baluwa jaki kwa kundumbali Chapanga (24-25). 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Nepani Yuda, mtumika waka Yesu Kristo na ndongu waka Yakobo. 
\p Nundembe mwehapa mwendowakiki na Chapanga na ambabhu mpalakiki na Chapanga Atati na kubhekakeka lukwale mkati jaka Yesu Kristo. 
\p  
\v 2 Nundobhela chiha, lukwali na upalu kwa maheli. 
\s1 Bhabhola bha upuhe 
\p  
\v 3 Bhakochi bhangu bhapalu, panakabhi ndenda ukangamalu namaa kundembela malobhi gha ukengaleku ambau nde witu tepani tabhokapi, nakaweni imbalika kundembela, nahuli kunjeghe mtima kubha njendalya na ukangamalu kwa ndandi ja uhobhalelu ambau Chapanga abhapekihi bhahuhu bhaki mala punkamu pena kwa chikahi chokapi.  
\v 4 Maghambu bhandu bhangakunjojabhe Chapanga bhalijingihi kwa sili pachilanda jitu, bhandu ambabhu kwa nyonjeka ja matamu ghabhu mahakau, bhang'anambula ubholu wa chihomu chaka Chapanga witu na kunkana Yesu Kristo joabhi kanjika jaki Chiongozi na Bambo witu Yesu Kristo. Nambu Malembu Mahuhu ghakajomwi kulotela kutumbu pamwandi hapa utemulu ghoubhalendalela bhandu bhanihabha. 
\p  
\v 5 Henu mbala kunkombukela mambu ghanihagha, hata ngati njomwili kughamanya mambu ghanihagha ghokapi, ja kubha Bambo paakajomwi kubhakengale bhandu ku inchi ja Misili, nambu panakatahi akabhayoningi bhandu bhala bhangakuhobhalela.  
\v 6 Na bhatumika bha kunani kumahunde ambabhu ngachebhakailendiki yeu yabhu, na kughaleka matamu ghabhu gha kutumbula, Chapanga abhakongiki mu lwihi kwa minyololo ja mileli bhatemuliwaje mu Lichobha lela likolongwa la utemulo.  
\v 7 Mkombukaje michi ja Sodoma na Gomola, na michi ja munkeghi jaki, bhenehi bhaki bhakatendiki ngati bhatumika bha kunani kumahunde bhala, bhakatendiki ukemi na mambu ghaghabhi chihanganyuma cha hyegha yabhu: Bhakapekiwi utemulo wa moto wa mileli, ukubha ulakalilu kwa bhandu bhokapi. 
\p  
\v 8 Bhenibhela nde mokubhelili kwa bhandu bhanihabha. Ndotu yabhu yalongoha mu kuihakaha hyegha yabhu bhene, bhajojoha lujiniku lwaka Chapanga na kuitondola ihumbi ihuhu ya kunani kumahunde hoku.  
\v 9 Hata Mikaeli, mtumika nkolongwa, ngacheakatendiki bhenibhela. Mu kulochana kola pachilanda jaki na Lijobhi panani ja hyegha jaka Musa, Mikaeli ngacheakalengiki kuntemula Lijobhi kwa matondu, nambu akapwaghiki: “Bambo mweni na akulakalyaje!”  
\v 10 Nambu bhandu bhanihabha bhaghatondola mambu ghokapi ghangakughamanya, anabhayonangikaje kwa mambu ghalaghala ghabhaghamanyi kwa umanyi wabhu bheni ngati hinyama yanga na malango, mambu ghanihagha nde nakanopi ghaghayonanga.  
\v 11 Anabhachibhonaje! Bhandu bhanihabha bhajengalili lujendu lolalola lwaka Kaini. Kwa ndandi ja mbija, bhalijingihi mu lihakau lelalela laka Balaamu. Bhakakaniki kutii ngati moakakani kutii Kola na bhatemuliwi ngati moakatemulaki Kola.  
\v 12 Bhandu bhanihabha bhakula papamu na mwehapa panga ihoni mu uwangalalu winu wa upalu. Bhalengana na bhadima bhabhalileha bheni pela, na bhabhi ngati mahundi ghangakubha na mache, ghaghagholuheka na mpongu. Bhombi nde ngati mikongu jejipolwiti jangakupambika mapambiku, jejitupuliwi na kujoma nakanopi.  
\v 13 Bhandu bhanihabha nde ngati majegha makolongwa gha bahali, na matendu ghabhu gha ihoni nde ngati mahuluhulu. Bhombi nde ngati ndondwa yeihobha ambabhu bhabhekakiki mileli pandu pa lwihi lukolongwa. 
\p  
\v 14 Najombi Enoki, ambaju nde hokolu wa saba kutumbula Adamu, akalotiki ana panani ja bhandu bhanihabha: “Njowanyaje! Bambo ahika papamu na bhahuhu bhaki maelufu kwa maelufu,  
\v 15 kubhatemula bhandu bhokapi, na kubhalapula bhokapi bhangakunjojabhe Chapanga kwa ndandi ja matendu ghabhu ghokapi mahakau ghabhakatendiki panga kuntopela Chapanga, na kwa ndandi ja malobhi ghokapi mahakau ambaghu bhandu bhahakau bhakumpwaghi Chapanga!” 
\p  
\v 16 Bhandu bhanihabha bhang'ong'uteka pamaheli, na kung'ola, bhajengalela utokulelu wabhu uhakau, bhalibhona na kubhalumbalila bhandu bhangi nakanopi kwa nyonjeka jabhu bheni. 
\s1 Malakalilu na malaghalakilu 
\p  
\v 17 Nambu mwehapa mabhakochi bhangu bhapalu, mkombukaje ghala ghamwalaghalakiwi pamwandi na mitumi bhaka Bambo witu Yesu Kristo.  
\v 18 Bhakumpwaghi: “Mu machobha gha kujomukela, anabhapitalyaje bhandu bhabhalongama, bhandu bhabhajengalela utokulelu wabhu uhakau.”  
\v 19 Bhombi nde bhabhaleta ulekanganu, bhandu bha maholalelu gha kindema, bhangakubha na Roho waka Chapanga.  
\v 20 Nambu mwehapa, bhakochi bhangu bhapalu, mlichengaje mabhete panani ja uhobhalelu winu uhuhu nakanopi. Mlobhaje kwa makili ghaka Roho Mhuhu,  
\v 21 na kutamakila mu upalu waka Chapanga, koni mkalendalya kwa chiheku chiha chaka Bambo witu Yesu Kristo nahuli andetaje mu womi wa mileli. 
\p  
\v 22 Mwabhonila chiha bhandu bhala bhabhabhi na choghoi,  
\v 23 mwakengalyaje kwa kubhanyakuha kuhuma mumoto; nambu kwa bhangi mbya na chiha papamu na kulilenda, mhakalyaje hata ingobhu yabhu yeihakihe kwa matokulelu ghabhu mahakau. 
\s1 Malobhu gha kulumbalila 
\p  
\v 24 Kwaki Chapanga joaweza kundenda ngamwihika kuhabhuka, na kundeta mwehapa panga mahakau mbaka palongi ja ulumbalilu waki kwa chiheku chikolongwa,  
\v 25 jombi joabhi Chapanga kanjika jaki, Mkengalela witu Yesu Kristo Bambo witu, ulumbalilu ubya najombi, na ukolongwa, na lujiniku, na makili, kutumbula mileli, na sajenu, na hata mileli! Amina.